image_analysis.description: A photograph of an interior storage or utility room. The central focus is a white wall containing two large, rectangular electrical panel covers. To the left of the panels, a red fire extinguisher is mounted on the wall. To the right, there is a storage area with metal shelving units holding rolls of fabric or rugs. A brown chair and several boxes, including a green one, are visible in the foreground and background. The lighting appears to be from an overhead fluorescent fixture.
image_analysis.layout: The image is a horizontal photograph. The left two-thirds are dominated by a white utility wall, while the right third shows a cluttered storage space.

stamps_or_markings: Evidence/Document tracking number EFTA00000358 in the bottom right corner.
Small warning/instruction labels above each electrical panel door (text illegible).

document_metadata.subject: Interior storage/utility area with electrical panels and fire extinguisher

notes: The text on the small warning labels above the panels and on the fire extinguisher is too small to read clearly. The labels on the panel doors identify them as 'PP-B SECT. 1' and 'PP-B SECT. 2'.
